						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="bold">Śaka 1520 (1599 A.D.)</hi></p>						

						<p>Fragmentary. Seems to record an endowment (details lost) by a person (name lost) of the Ātrēya-gōtra and Āpastamba-sūtra. The details of the date viz. <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1520, Vikārin, Mithuna ba. 3, Friday, Uttirāḍam correspond to 1599 A.D. June 1, Friday, ·55; ·67. The Śaka year cited is however wrong for 1521</hi></p>						

